## Commercial License

For commercial licensing options that do not require compliance with the
AGPL v3 (including the network use disclosure requirement), please contact:

    licensing@zevaro.ai

Commercial licenses are available for organizations that:
- Cannot comply with AGPL v3 open source requirements
- Require proprietary modifications without source disclosure
- Need to integrate Zevaro-Core into closed-source products
- Want dedicated support and indemnification

## Which License Applies?

- If you use this software over a network, you must make the complete
  source code available to users under AGPL v3, OR obtain a commercial license.
- If you modify this software and distribute it, you must release your
  modifications under AGPL v3, OR obtain a commercial license.
- If neither condition applies to your use case, you may use this software
  under AGPL v3 at no cost.

